      "Configurable bus interfaces: AXI4, Wishbone, AHB-Lite, simple bus",
      "Linux capable with MMU plugin (boots Linux on LiteX, Arty A7)",
      "FPGA optimized: 240 MHz on Artix-7, 70 MHz on iCE40",
      "JTAG debug support via plugin",
      "Written in SpinalHDL, generates Verilog for synthesis"
    ]
